Package org.opengrok.indexer.history

Class HistoryClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • org.opengrok.indexer.history.HistoryClassLoader
  • public class HistoryClassLoader
extends ClassLoader
    Temporary hack to prevent XMLDecoder to deserialize other than allowed classes. This tries to prevent calling of methods on ProcessBuilder or Runtime (or similar) which could be used for code execution.
